{"tid":1745351,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"何文田常樂區手足入一入黎唔該！！","createTime":"2019-11-22T07:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T00:27:40.000Z","uid":337901,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8f9ee14ba326e9adf35ba0430231da3722d935c8","tid":1745351,"uid":337901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n拜託咁多位巴絲聽日24號全投<strong>2號傑仔</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絕對絕對唔可以再比民賤聯「懶蛇光」連任啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆你個街當選呢十幾年黎完全無撚過見過你泡頭，靠埋哂蛇齋餅糭昆鴆D廢老。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過知道大家都好唔中意白鴿黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但傑仔係呢一區十幾年既努力，大家都有目共睹，我地要踢走保皇，光復何文田<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XnWOyAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXnWOyAS.jpg&h=a0b6a404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係候選人臨入閘前一日殺出左個<strong>3號吳嘉輝</strong>，呢條友真係唔知做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無啦啦空降常樂，打住「五大訴求」旗號參選，sorry我真係睇唔到你有誠意幫我地年青人入立法會進行抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係呢個幾月我完全無見過你擺街站，屌你老尾連聯絡方法都無，點信你啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人血饅頭好唔好食啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nK0S0eU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnK0S0eU.jpg&h=de087629&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99NBHtf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99NBHtf.jpg&h=b102509a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n況且.......你係民賤聯B隊，都唔洗咁明顯話自己參選既，連字體都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係我踢爆你架，係你自己踢爆自己咋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLink：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191115/60259440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191115%2F60259440&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=0d93a96d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191115%2F60259440&h=d4997836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191115/60259440</a><br />\n<br />\n收到風你提名名單入面好似有民建聯義工做提名人窩🤭唔知係你冒簽啊，還是民賤聯安排你黎鎅票呢，相信常樂區街坊的眼睛都是雪亮的<br />\n<br />\n最後：<br />\n<br />\n24號星期日，拜託大家全家總動員全投2號傑仔！！！仲有！！！早D去投票啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"979d2549ecddf61d89eca9dff4013d614a7ff43c","tid":1745351,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78f10db1cffde17dca06c1800a2a456b4c098007","tid":1745351,"uid":75575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f9ee14ba326e9adf35ba0430231da3722d935c8","tid":1745351,"uid":337901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n拜託咁多位巴絲聽日24號全投<strong>2號傑仔</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絕對絕對唔可以再比民賤聯「懶蛇光」連任啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆你個街當選呢十幾年黎完全無撚過見過你泡頭，靠埋哂蛇齋餅糭昆鴆D廢老。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過知道大家都好唔中意白鴿黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但傑仔係呢一區十幾年既努力，大家都有目共睹，我地要踢走保皇，光復何文田<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"h